---
const title = "My Journey | Akash Astrologic";
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{title}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --gold: #d4af37; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #fff; margin: 0; 
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.85), rgba(0,0,0,0.85)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1502134249126-9f3755a50d78?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');
            background-size: cover; background-attachment: fixed; line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .container { max-width: 850px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        
        /* Fixed 5-Page Nav */
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 20px; padding: 25px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); margin-bottom: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        nav a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        nav a:hover { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); }
        
        .story-card { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); padding: 45px; border-radius: 35px; border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2); }
        h1 { color: var(--gold); font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 25px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); padding-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; }
        
        .highlight { color: var(--gold); font-weight: bold; }
        .quote-box { border-left: 4px solid var(--gold); margin: 35px 0; font-style: italic; font-size: 1.25rem; background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1); padding: 25px; border-radius: 0 25px 25px 0; color: #eee; }
        
        .footer-cta { margin-top: 60px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top: 40px; }
        .btn-wa { color: #25D366; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">Journey</a>
            <a href="/services">Services</a>
            <a href="/reviews">Reviews</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="story-card">
            <h1>The Journey</h1>
            
            <p>I didn't start in a temple. It started with a simple question: <span class="highlight">"Why do some people work 10x harder but get 10x less?"</span></p>

            <div class="quote-box">
                "I realized that hard work is only half the equation. The other half is timing."
            </div>

            <p>While the world was looking at logic alone, i began to study the <span class="highlight">unseen patterns</span> of the universe. After years of analyzing thousands of charts and serving as an expert on <strong>AstroSage</strong>, i decoded the "Cosmic Blueprint".</p>

            <p>Today, <span class="highlight">Akash Astrologic</span> serves as a bridge between ancient wisdom and the modern strategist. My mission is to give u the ultimate advantage: <span class="highlight">Logic to Light.</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-cta">
            <p>Ready to align with your destiny?</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/918580672809" class="btn-wa"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Message me on WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
